source.name: Colorado Plateau Rapid Ecoregion Assessment Terrestrial Intactness and Potential For Change
source.description: This map shows current and near-term terrestrial intactness, as well as long term potential for development and climate change.  These datasets are the results of a series of fuzzy logic models that integrate many landscape factors, including urban, agriculture, roads, invasive vegetation, and fire regime.
